{"tid":470447,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"性別承認制度 - 男可以變女，女可以變男，無需做變性手術。","createTime":"2017-11-16T10:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T21:00:45.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c53d513759c8307640466ddfdca7ccd109d07db","tid":470447,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"有機會通過的話，將來香港身份證，都變成藍絲，和紅巴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iwggr.gov.hk/chi/pdf/eSummary.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwggr.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2FeSummary.pdf&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5cd55bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.iwggr.gov.hk/chi/pdf/eSummary.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.scs.org.hk/2017/09/08/性別承認議題公眾諮詢-faq1：基本概念和背景資料/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.scs.org.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%B0%E9%A1%8C%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-faq1%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%2F&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5dbf870d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.scs.org.hk/2017/09/08/性別承認議題公眾諮詢-faq1：基本概念和背景資料/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171031/20199683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199683&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=e9f93f51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199683&h=f235fdeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171031/20199683</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果身份證可以變性，諮詢文件根據世界各地的法律制度，列出有以下四種模式。<br />\n<br />\n（如果自我聲明模式獲得通過，任何身份證上的性別，都可以做藍絲，紅巴）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「自我聲明模式」：准許申請人聲明自己屬某一性別便可更改性別身份，而不設任何醫療干預或個人身份的限制，也不涉任何複雜的程序。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「無需手術模式」：無須接受變性手術，但需一些醫學證據，如性別焦躁的診斷及「實際生活體驗」證明等；<br />\n<br />\n「規定手術模式」：規定須接受變性手術，但較少其他醫學證據方面的規定；<br />\n<br />\n「較多限制模式」：要求已進行性別重置手術、提交醫學診斷證明及排除已婚人士的申請等。<br />\n<br />\n問題：「自我聲明模式」看起來好像怪怪的，真的甚麼條件都不需要嗎？<br />\n<br />\n答案：「自我聲明模式」基本上是「當事人說了算」，甚麼客觀證據和條件也不需要，可能有點匪夷所思，但現時已有一些真實例子：<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷(2012)、丹麥(2014)、馬爾他(2015)、愛爾蘭(2015)、挪威(2016)、法國(2017)及比利時(2017)<br />\n丹麥已採納自我聲明模式，「申請人只需作自我聲明屬何性別，該聲明不會被質疑。沒有醫學專家的介入，也不會對申請人的心理和身體健康作評估。」（《諮詢文件》，頁98）只需要半年時間等待，這「等候期是避免人們因倉卒決定而後悔莫及」。<br />\n<br />\n挪威的方案容許小至六歲兒童，在父母同意下改變性別身份，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超過16歲則可隨自己意願改變，不用醫療證明，而且網上已可辦理，手續簡便猶如改名。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"996497c942e0c878978a39721161e0f7383d64e5","tid":470447,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"好呀，一次過解決女權問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b130e7e5197b28f76919663597341166c885a07","tid":470447,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"又黎料"},{"pid":"7a0e95ef58cae7bbf924db0de47b68925b407366","tid":470447,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"咁入邊個廁所"},{"pid":"755b4a1a618524542a0ec5dc80e5c968bca00e97","tid":470447,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"on99<br />\n天生係咁就話悲劇<br />\n宜家呢啲擺明歪曲事實 矯枉過正 無限放大左膠歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗極之少數有雙性人病 天生就只有男同女<br />\n有j就男 有西就女 冇得後天改變<br />\n就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbbd09592a92ac6a040a36abda77c90a22fef69","tid":470447,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"但男女廁又點分<br />\n以後女廁有尿兜？"},{"pid":"61a6e35343191fac2a4a61ad839aadb20eddcfe7","tid":470447,"uid":35429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:53:40.